                    Biber. Sacrum. Profanum
                </h2>
                <h4>
                    A Sensual Play of Contrasts
                </h4>
                <p  class="projekt-text-p">
                    From mysticism to the pulse of the streets—music that seduces and surprises. Biber. Sacrum. Profanum. is a program that boldly plays with the boundary between the sacred and the profane. Immersed in folk rhythms, Biber’s sonatas intertwine spirituality and sensuality in unexpected places. This is a story full of intensity—sensual, rebellious, and at times mystical. It is a journey of raw energy, where every sound becomes an impulse for creation on stage—from lively, tavern-like atmospheres to the deepest moments of the sacred. In this program, we celebrate the beauty and unpredictability of Baroque contrasts, creating a space for both reflection and the sheer joy of music that transcends time and imagination.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="projekt-2-down">
            <div id="bg-eclipse">
