                    <li>H.I.F. von Biber - Mystery Sonata “The Assumption of the Virgin”</li>
                    <li>H.I.F. von Biber - Sonata in F major C 140</li>
                    <li>H.I.F. von Biber - Mystery Sonata "The Annunciation"</li>
                    <li>H.I.F. von Biber - Sonata in C minor C 143</li>
                    <li>H.I.F. von Biber - Mystery Sonata "The Crucifixion"</li>
                </ul>
