                    La Stella
                </h2>
                <h4>
                    A Musical Rebellion
                </h4>
                <p class="projekt-text-p">
                    An eccentric genius who knew no limits—Giovanni Antonio Pandolfi Mealli. If you’re looking for something unforgettable, La Stella is the project for you. His sonatas from Op. 4 are a whirlwind of constantly shifting emotions—a musical tornado that is wild, passionate, and full of intensity. Dedicated to the composer’s friends and acquaintances, these pieces are not just personal confessions but a sonic extravagance that captivates from the very first note to the last. Our latest project, dedicated to Pandolfi Mealli, premiered at the Gregoriana Sastamala Festival in Finland. It is a musical journey into the eccentric world of Baroque.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="projekt-3-down">
