                    SPLEEN
                </h2>
                <h4>
                    Autumn Melancholy
                </h4>
                <p class="projekt-text-p">
                    Baroque melancholy with unexpected twists. SPLEEN is a journey through sound from the mid-17th to the 18th century, exploring the key of D minor in all its shades and possibilities. This program brings together virtuosic pieces filled with raw emotion, inspired by the wistful mood of autumn and the legendary Krakowski Spleen by Kora.
                    Each piece is an invitation to an inner journey, offering both introspection and joy. SPLEEN blends deep emotions with uplifting energy, touching the heart and revealing the beauty of Baroque forms. Every fragment encourages reflection, balancing depth with lightness, moving both the heart and mind in unexpected ways.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
